quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  52,1,"Mi woondirii [Fello] Tuuri ngon"
  52,2,E Deftere winndaande nden
  52,3,e Й—eri fontaaЙ—i
  52,4,E Suudu wuurniraandu ndun
  52,5,E Kippoodi toowundi ndin
  52,6,E maayo heewuno ngon
  52,7,"Pellet, lepte Joomi maa Й—en ko yanooje"
  52,8,Alaa duГұoowo Й—e
  52,9,Г‘alnde kammu ngun dillirta dillere
  52,10,pelle Й—en wona e yahugol
  52,11,"haray nden Гұalnde, bone woodanii fennuЙ“e Й“en"
  52,12,"Й“en wonuЙ“e e jumpugol, hiЙ“e fija"
  52,13,Г‘alnde Й“e duГұiroytee doole ka Yiite Jahannama duГұannde
  52,14,"[ЖҒe wi'anee] : \"Ko ngee Yiite woni ko fennaynoЙ—on"
  52,15,E ko mbilewu nii? Kaa hara on alaa yi'ude
  52,16,"Sumee e magge! MuГұГұiЙ—on maa on muГұГұaaki, fow no fota e mon. Anndee ko yoЙ“eteЙ—on, ko kon ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  52,17,"Pellet, gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en hino e Aljannaaji e neemaaji"
  52,18,"ko Й“e dakimitotooЙ“e kon ko Joomi maЙ“Й“e okki Й“e, Joomi maЙ“Й“e daЙ—ndi Й“e lepte Jahiimi Й—en"
  52,19,"[ЖҒe wi'anee] : \"Г‘aamee yaron, ko newi moЙ—deum, sabu kon ko gollaynoЙ—on"
  52,20,"hara ko on soЙ“Й“indiiЙ“e e hoore danЙ—e weertindiraaЙ—e\", Men resina Й“e kadi yooЙ—a e yaaJa giteeЙ“e"
  52,21,"ЖҒen gomЙ—imЙ“e, geyngol maЙ“Й“e ngol kadi jokki Й“e e gomЙ—inal, Men tawtindinay Й“e e geyngol maЙ“Й“e ngol. Men Й—uytantaa Й“e huunde e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en; neЙ—Й—o kala ko faggitii kon no tiginaa"
  52,22,Men Й“eydani Й“e muuyanteeЙ—i e tebbeeli kala ko tuuyetee
  52,23,"HiЙ“e jaaЙ“ondira ton, ГұedduЙ—e Й—e jillaa meere wanaa ko bakkondinta"
  52,24,"SukaaЙ“e no eltanaaЙ“e hino wanngoo hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, wa'uЙ“e wa kaЕӢЕӢe maraaЙ—e"
  52,25,"Yoga maЙ“Й“e fewtita yoga, Й“e lamndondira"
  52,26,"Й“e wi'a: \"Pellet, men laatino ado [hannde], hulunooЙ“e [lepte Й—en] hakkunde yimЙ“e amen"
  52,27,"Allah moЖҙЖҙii e amen, O daЙ—ni men lepte Norngal"
  52,28,"Men laatino ado [hannde], torotonooЙ“e Mo. Pellet, ko Kanko woni MoЖҙЖҙo, HinnotooЙ—o On"